---
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Jynalis Diaz | Aspiring SOC Analyst</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        background-color: #10172b;
        color: #e0e0e0;
        font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        padding: 60px 80px;
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        line-height: 1.7;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .hero {
        text-align: center;
        padding-bottom: 60px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #54bec4;
      }

      .name {
        font-size: 2.8rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #ffffff;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        overflow: hidden;
        white-space: nowrap;
        border-right: 3px solid #54bec4;
        width: fit-content;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: block;
        animation: typing 2s steps(12, end) forwards,
                   blink 0.75s step-end infinite;
      }

      @keyframes typing {
        from { width: 0 }
        to { width: 100% }
      }

      @keyframes blink {
        from, to { border-color: transparent }
        50% { border-color: #54bec4 }
      }

      .title {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #54bec4;
        margin-top: 10px;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadein 0.5s ease 2s forwards;
      }

      .cursor {
        display: inline-block;
        color: #54bec4;
        animation: blink 0.75s step-end infinite;
      }

      .section {
        margin-top: 56px;
      }

      .section-header {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.25em;
        color: #54bec4;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #1a2a3a;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .intro {
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #b0b0b0;
        max-width: 620px;
        border-left: 2px solid #54bec4;
        padding-left: 18px;
        opacity: 0;
        font-style: italic;
        animation: fadein 0.5s ease 2.5s forwards;
      }

      .placeholder {
        color: #2e4a5a;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-style: italic;
      }

      .folder {
        background-color: #0d1a2a;
        border: 1px solid #1e3a4a;
        border-radius: 6px;
        overflow: hidden;
        transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
      }

      .folder:hover {
        border-color: #54bec4;
      }

      .folder-tab {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        padding: 14px 18px;
        cursor: pointer;
        user-select: none;
      }

      .folder-name {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: #54bec4;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      }

      .folder-arrow {
        margin-left: auto;
        color: #54bec4;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        transition: transform 0.2s ease;
      }

      .folder.open .folder-arrow {
        transform: rotate(90deg);
      }

      .folder-contents {
        display: none;
        padding: 0 18px 18px 18px;
        border-top: 1px solid #1e3a4a;
      }

      .folder.open .folder-contents {
        display: block;
      }

      .project-card {
        display: flex;
        gap: 18px;
        margin-top: 18px;
        background-color: #0a0e1a;
        border: 1px solid #1a2a3a;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 16px;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .project-thumbnail {
        width: 120px;
        height: 80px;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 3px;
        border: 1px solid #1e3a4a;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }

      .project-info {
        flex: 1;
      }

      .project-title {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #ffffff;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }

      .project-desc {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: #b0b0b0;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .project-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 8px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .badge {
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        padding: 3px 10px;
        border-radius: 2px;
        text-decoration: none;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        border: 1px solid #54bec4;
        color: #54bec4;
        transition: background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
      }

      .badge:hover {
        background-color: #54bec4;
        color: #0a0e1a;
      }

      .contact-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        margin-top: 8px;
      }

      .status {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        background-color: #0d1f2d;
        color: #54bec4;
        padding: 4px 14px;
        border-radius: 2px;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        margin-top: 56px;
        border: 1px solid #54bec4;
      }

      .status-dot {
        display: inline-block;
        width: 7px;
        height: 7px;
        background-color: #54bec4;
        border-radius: 50%;
        margin-right: 6px;
        animation: pulse 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      @keyframes pulse {
        0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
        50% { opacity: 0.2; }
      }

      @keyframes fadein {
        from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(6px); }
        to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <div class="hero">
      <div class="name">Jynalis Diaz</div>
      <div class="title">Aspiring SOC Analyst <span class="cursor">_</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-header">whoami</div>
      <p class="intro">
        I got into this through an SQL class that ended up changing everything.
        Started exploring, found SOC work, and it just clicked, it's the kind
        of work that encourages me to want to keep learning. I'm a recent grad,
        actively looking for my first role, and this site is where I document
        what I'm building along the way.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-header">Current Work</div>
      <p class="placeholder">// SOC projects in progress, check back soon ;)</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-header">personal projects</div>
      <div class="folder" id="folder-personal">
        <div class="folder-tab">
          <span>📁</span>
          <span class="folder-name">personal_projects/</span>
          <span class="folder-arrow">▶</span>
        </div>
        <div class="folder-contents">
          <div class="project-card">
            <img
              src="/UI of detection tool.png"
              alt="Fake Job Posting Detection Tool UI"
              class="project-thumbnail"
            />
            <div class="project-info">
              <div class="project-title">Fake Job Posting Detection Tool</div>
              <p class="project-desc">
                A detection and education tool that analyzes job postings for fraud
                indicators using Logistic Regression + TF-IDF. Built to not just flag
                suspicious postings but explain why they're suspicious, helping
                students recognize scams over time.
              </p>
              <div class="project-links">
                <a href="https://github.com/GinaBuilds/Senior-Capstone-Project-Spring-2026" target="_blank" class="badge">[ GitHub ]</a>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jynalis-diaz-323b632b6/" target="_blank" class="badge">[ LinkedIn ]</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-header">need to reach me?</div>
      <div class="contact-links">
        <a href="https://x.com/JynalisCyber" target="_blank" class="badge">[ x.com/JynalisCyber ]</a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jynalis-diaz-323b632b6/" target="_blank" class="badge">[ LinkedIn ]</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <span class="status">
        <span class="status-dot"></span>SITE ACTIVE
      </span>
    </div>

    <script>
      document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
        document.querySelectorAll('.folder-tab').forEach(tab => {
          tab.addEventListener('click', () => {
            const folder = tab.closest('.folder');
            if (folder) folder.classList.toggle('open');
          });
        });
      });
    </script>

  </body>
</html>